        <num>CC 1532</num>
        <heading>1532.  Stipulation for right of return to donor</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1532.  Stipulation for right of return to donor
The donor may stipulate the right of return of the thing given, either in the case of his surviving the donee only, or in the case of his surviving the donee and the descendants of the donee.
The right may be stipulated only for the advantage of the donor.</p>
        </content>
